Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110214,114093}She's an angel!\NIt's like an angel is riding a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114093,117347}I've never seen such a beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117805,119849}I wish I were that horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120600,122852}I'll be the horse's rear legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:07.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123978,127815}An angel?! If she had wings,\Nshe wouldn't have to ride on the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127815,129108}They're so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129108,131819}Rear legs? Is he talking about\Na two-man horse in a play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132654,135406}What about a two-man\Nhorse in a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135406,137116}It's stupid boy-talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137116,139494}They're talking about\Nthe princess of their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:22.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139494,142872}There's a mansion\Non their way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:27.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142872,147126}In the large yard, there's a lady\Nwho gracefully rides a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:30.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147126,150421}The boys are admiring her\Nand call her their "Madonna".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150421,153549}They sneak by to watch her\Nevery day on their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:34.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153549,154926}How perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154926,156552}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157261,160556}{\i1}I wonder if Asuka Jr.\Ngoes there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161224,163393}Is she that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163393,165269}What?! You haven't seen her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165269,166479}– No.\N– Well, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166479,168773}I can take you there today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169649,171275}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171275,172735}I'm not that interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:58.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173986,178700}Man! Asuka's head is filled\Nonly with thoughts of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.21,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:186374,189210}Return the Thoroughbred!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204475,205601}You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222577,226330}What?! She was cheated and lost the horse\Nthat the boys were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226748,229625}Yes. The horse's name is Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:54.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230793,234380}Both Billy's father and mother\Nwere very famous racehorses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234380,236299}He's a top-notch Thoroughbred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:01.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237008,241596}But that Madonna, rather, Ms. Maki Nishina\Nwas against turning him into a racehorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241596,243765}So he became a riding horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248102,251022}That's a very extravagant\Nthing to do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251022,254817}If he's so famous,\Nhe's worth quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254817,257028}Like they say, she must be\Nan extremely rich princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:22.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257028,262533}Yes. And according to some people,\Nshe's wasting a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:29.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263534,269665}A man named Soma kept visiting\NMaki's house asking her to sell Billy to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270374,273753}But Maki flatly refused his offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273753,276631}But Soma wouldn't\Ngive up, and one day…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291479,294565}Whoa! Whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295608,298069}Well, hello, Lady Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298444,299904}I won't sell Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299904,302031}My answer won't change,\Nno matter how many times you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302240,303825}Now, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:08.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304617,308996}I've got a wonderful idea\Nthat may appeal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309956,312458}First, please look at this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314460,316045}He's Wild Bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316045,317672}He's from a very famous bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:23.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319674,323886}He is as good as your Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:29.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324554,329851}This horse isn't a bad trade for Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330142,333187}Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333187,334814}I love Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335231,337775}I'll never give him\Nto someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:50.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349620,350496}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351414,352498}What's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354000,355501}It's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358170,360506}What are you going to do?\NHis leg is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365011,370433}The medical report Soma brought definitely\Nstated that the leg was broken, Maki said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:15.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370808,375897}I've heard that a broken leg is the same\Nas a death sentence for a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:23.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375897,383571}Yes. That's why Soma demanded Billy\Nin exchange, as if he had the right to take Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:27.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383571,387909}She said her father couldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388117,390036}But something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390036,392788}Things were\Ntoo convenient for Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392788,395541}Only Soma is winning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396459,397376}You mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397919,400880}Yes. Maki is thinking that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400880,403966}She thinks they were\Nset up from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403966,406594}Soma wanted Billy very badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:50.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406594,410848}And the horse's broken leg was\Nsupported only by the medical report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411515,414977}He tricked them in order to get Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414977,418314}He had no intention\Nof giving up his horse, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419106,421651}Maki thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:06.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421651,426906}She thinks they somehow surprised Billy\Nand made him fall into that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426906,429283}Yes! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:14.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429825,434705}But Soma has already\Nbecome the legal owner of Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434705,438250}Billy and Maki\Nwill never be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438376,439377}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439377,442546}Under such circumstances,\NSt. Tail can get the horse back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442546,445216}In addition, I'll reveal\NSoma's evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:32.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446634,452223}But Billy is already scheduled\Nto go to a ranch in Hokkaido tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452223,453599}And by train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453599,454934}Train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:38.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455476,458646}It's the K-Express,\Nleaving Seika Station at 8:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458646,460982}We have only four hours\Nuntil its departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:41.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460982,461899}Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473786,475830}What short notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475830,477915}Did he go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477915,479291}How can I send him a warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480042,481794}Hey, have you seen Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482461,484380}No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:06.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484380,486424}Didn't he go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486424,487967}Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:11.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490386,491762}There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491762,494265}It may be a bit much,\Nbut I guess I should use that method.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:32.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506193,512616}"Tonight I'll get Billy from the K-Express train\Nleaving Seika Station at 8:02."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513284,515036}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515036,516162}It's a warning note…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516912,518581}That's quite something…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518998,521042}Dad! Let me borrow\Nyour train schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521042,523044}The one you always\Nuse for your trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523044,524545}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526547,527506}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527506,529008}Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:53.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529550,533471}But why do you need it, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534055,535848}Well… for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539935,540644}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:01.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540644,541604}– Mom!\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541604,543439}Is Meimi going on a trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543439,546025}Not that I know of.\NI haven't heard anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546025,548611}I wonder if she's running away…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:13.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549653,553574}If so, she wouldn't borrow\Nthe schedule from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554742,556535}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556911,559997}There are a lot of things\Ngoing on at her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561332,563959}It's a difficult age…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:31.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568214,571884}Let's see…\Nthe K-Express departs at 8:02…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572343,574386}It will pass that point at…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576597,577807}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.26,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:577807,580267}Seika Station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611006,612091}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:15.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612508,615261}St. Tail is coming to steal Billy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615261,616220}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616220,619431}We'll be aboard the train\Nto protect the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619431,620558}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622977,624562}Here comes the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637658,641453}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646125,647459}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649628,651130}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652840,654675}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:14.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670649,674153}May the blessings of God be with us.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:22.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:682703,682703}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:27.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:687708,687708}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692379,694715}There are no suspicious\Npersons on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695174,696383}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696383,698385}Position yourselves at each place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699845,701680}No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701931,704141}Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704141,706143}What's the commotion,\NMr. Soma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:51.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707311,711565}Well, this young lady\Nwas doing a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:55.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711565,715611}She was trying to open the door\Nof the livestock car and let Billy escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720699,722660}I beg you! Please return Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724036,726205}You're going too far, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726205,728249}Billy is mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728249,731043}You don't have the right\Nto even touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731293,732503}Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732503,734672}I know you set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734672,736674}There was no way Billy\Nwould get upset like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736674,738008}You made him upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738676,741804}He made Billy upset?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741804,743973}Don't say something so stupid\Nwithout any evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744640,746183}Never come close to this horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747726,749687}Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750312,753023}Who on earth are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754692,755651}Billy…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771583,773085}Billy! Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775045,776130}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779174,780134}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:00.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780175,780968}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781010,782094}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785848,787099}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796317,797276}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801989,803282}Billy…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805284,806994}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812541,815544}I see. I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815544,818505}I'm not doing anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818505,822217}I suppose that girl\Ncan't let go of Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:47.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822676,827181}But St. Tail always has\Na good reason for stealing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:52.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829099,832144}Rather than worrying about that,\Nhow about your security?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832144,834646}Even that girl was able to get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836065,837941}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:03.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837941,843113}We have one officer on each car and\Ntwo officers in front of the livestock car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844031,845741}I'll be at the livestock car, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845741,848494}So it's impossible to break in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848494,849912}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854375,856043}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873477,875729}First, check the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887074,888826}{\i1}That must be Soma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,890661}{\i1}I wonder what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891161,894581}Darn! Why is Billy singled out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894581,897251}St. Tail wants him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897251,899628}That means Billy\Nis a very good horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900379,903757}Of course he is!\NThat's the reason I fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905134,906927}He'll bring us a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906927,909138}But that was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909138,911348}You invented\NWild Bunch's broken leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911348,914560}You blamed it on Billy,\Nand then you got him for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:21.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916270,921024}The key was to use the fact\Nthat the girl didn't want to sell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921024,923777}coupled with your special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939251,941795}{\i1}It's like we thought.\NThat's how they did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941795,944715}{\i1}Now that we know,\NI'll take Billy no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951722,953682}{\i1}The livestock car is the very last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:57.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953682,957060}{\i1}Naturally, Asuka Jr.\Nis keeping it under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957060,958270}{\i1}If that's the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962191,964026}How's it going?\NIs there anything unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964026,966069}No. Nothing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966069,967571}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981668,983962}This is Asuka! I've found St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983962,986048}Everyone! Get up on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989760,991011}Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:36.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991637,996016}I was checking it out and there's no officer\Nin the next car or anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996016,997976}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997976,1000896}What's going on?\NWhat happened to the kid, Asuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000896,1003941}I didn't see him, either.\NMaybe something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005234,1007069}I'm worried about Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:47.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007069,1007778}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007778,1008862}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010239,1013075}Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014201,1017079}Give up now!\NThere's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024127,1025295}{\i1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:11.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025295,1031510}{\i1}Isn't it strange that St. Tail shows up\Nin the front when Billy is in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038850,1039851}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041728,1044273}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045315,1046775}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058453,1060289}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068297,1070299}Shoot! Someone's on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078223,1079891}Like we thought, it's St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080142,1081893}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083270,1084855}Ignore him! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096575,1098869}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098869,1101038}Get off of me!\NGet off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101038,1102539}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104791,1106293}Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107169,1109254}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123310,1124936}St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135280,1136073}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136657,1138075}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138408,1141078}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150545,1151755}She was all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157219,1159471}What a stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159471,1161723}I'll definitely catch you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:27.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163517,1167896}I'll let you see your pretty lady soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:30.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169439,1170899}What's the matter, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186498,1187624}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191044,1191586}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192421,1193463}Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212065,1214192}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214609,1217738}Soma's wrongdoing was\Nrevealed to the police, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218697,1221908}So Billy is formally returned to Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223201,1224953}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224953,1227080}But it's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227080,1229833}He made up the story about the broken leg\Nand faked the medical report,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229833,1232836}and he upset Billy\Nby hitting him with a BB.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232836,1235338}Really! I can't believe it!
